data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Discover this property, showcasing a delightful residence situated on a generous 0.25-acre parcel. Inside, you'll find a welcoming living area complete with a charming brick wood-burning fireplace, an elegant formal dining room, & a generously proportioned family room. The basement adds an intriguing hidden gem that is a must-see! Upstairs, you'll find two full bathrooms accompanying the bedrooms. Outside, the backyard boasts ample room, including a garden, storage shed, & parking for RV/Boat. A must see!
